          "description": "If I could give no stars i would. All of the bad reviews for this are deserved. I came her for an emergency room visit and was completely ignored repeatedly. The staff here spend more time giggling and talking to each other than they do with their patience. Waited for my son to come back from a CT scan for 2 hours. Three doctors triage him one after the other with no idea of the information given prior. They discharged my son with out telling anyone. No one communicates with the patience. For 3-4 hours no one spoke to me about anything.  Shift changed and no one introduced themselves to let you know who will be handling your care. Thos place is horrible. I would rather go to Lincoln hospital instead of here and Lincoln hospital is known for killing people. They only way to n get result is to be irate or angry and loud for someone to pay attention to you or give a care. This place should not be training future doctors. The training here would greatly impact the health care industry in a negative way. This is like high school here. The giggle and talk to each other but do only part of their work. HORRIBLE PLACE. ADDITUDE CENTRAL. POOR BEDSIDE MANOR. POOR COMMUNICTORS. LAZY PASSING THE BUCK STAFF.",
