          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLfaGueU91Jv8xhlOUXkRg8ZiB9SOs1w-66edzKOmfEhc2BMpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "It's official , this hospital is a mess .\nI arrived at the emergency entrance with a head injury,  checked in and waited a couple of hours before my name was called . I was then taken to a area to do additional check in and then was seated in a\n\"fast track \" area that was actually disorganized and slow .\nThree patients who arrived after me were seen before me and when I pointed this out to a hospital employee I eventually was seen by a Doctor.\nThe Doctor ordered a CT Scan and hours went by but no one from Radiology came to retrieve me , although the Radiology Dept was picking up people that came after me. The disorganization was amazing , Radiology came to pick up a person who canceled their CT scan  30 minutes earlier but they were still unable to take me.\nI complained again , I asked for the Doctor,  I asked for the Manager,  the Doctor arrived and proceeded to expedite my CT Scan .\nThe Radiology Dept never came to pick me up , the Doctor personally took me over . It appears that my CT scan was ordered and mysteriously canceled,  why?? , by who??\nAfter the CT Scan , no one came to escort me back to the Fast Track area therefore the Radiologist had to do it . I was the longest patient waiting that came through  ER on the day that I was there.\nThe Doctor was great but the hospital is a mess .\nPS . The manager never showed up to speak to me .",
